# sdwan_cisco_vpn_feature_template (Data Source)

This data source can read the Cisco VPN feature template.

## Example Usage

```terraform
data "sdwan_cisco_vpn_feature_template" "example" {
  id = "f6b2c44c-693c-4763-b010-895aa3d236bd"
}
```
